description: This file provides mechanisms to access the OpenAI API key from environment variables and acts as a placeholder for future API calls to OpenAI. It includes functions to retrieve the API key set via environment variables and a stub for making API requests.

methods.name: getOpenAIApiKey()
methods.description: Returns the OpenAI API key from environment variables if set; otherwise, undefined.

methods.name: callOpenAI(params)
methods.description: Placeholder function for making an API call to OpenAI, not yet implemented, throws an error if called.
